criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  consecutive cases of colorectal polyps and submucosal lesions with anticipated
             complete removal endoscopically by EMR.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  severe cardiovascular diseases, liver and kidney dysfunction;

          -  platelet and coagulation dysfunction (PLT < 50*109/L, INR > 2);

          -  cases that have taken anticoagulant drugs or non-steroidal anti-inflammatory drugs
             within 1 month before the procedure;

          -  cases unavailable for follow-up.
